data.description: UPGRADES GALORE!!! NEW CARPET! CERAMIC TILE! UPDATED BATHROOMS! ENTIRE UNIT FRESHLY PAINTED!!!  Welcome home! As you enter this spacious two bedroom unit you'll find new carpet throughout, a large living room and separate dining room area.   Relax in the living in front of the gas fireplace.  Fireplace allows you to mount any size TV under 50 inches.  A spacious kitchen area with counter top which can be used as an alternative bar top from the dining area.  The dining area leads out to the patio.  Step into the master bedroom where you'll find a spacious area which leads into your oasis of an updated master bathroom to include updated cabinets, jacuzzi and separate shower.  Next, take a view of the second bedroom with spacious area and bay window.   Ceiling fans in both bedrooms.  Updated bathroom outside of the 2nd bedroom to include ceramic tile and updated cabinets.  Sellers are motivated to sell, present your best offer. Offers will be presented to the owner on Monday at noon.   Property is sold as is and is not FHA approved.
